# @param {Integer[]} battery_percentages
# @return {Integer}
def count_tested_devices(battery_percentages)
    tested_devices = 0
    
    battery_percentages.each_with_index do |percentage, i|
        if percentage > 0
            tested_devices += 1
            # Decrease the battery percentage of all devices starting from the next index
            (i + 1...battery_percentages.length).each do |j|
                battery_percentages[j] = [0, battery_percentages[j] - 1].max
            end
        end
    end
    
    tested_devices
end
